{"tid":306363,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術討論]究竟肥婆係點做愛？","createTime":"2017-07-02T13:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T21:24:40.000Z","uid":52728,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"21f354efee47823027ae832a0fcdcfc284ebe0a4","tid":306363,"uid":52728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T13:00:06.000Z","msg":"有無巴打可以話我知肥婆係點做愛？<br />\n雖然可能真係有人係有鋪癮，但我諗左好耐都諗唔到肥婆可以做到愛嘅可能性？<br />\n<br />\n其實對脾咁多肉會唔會阻住搞到入唔到<br />\n二嚟究竟點摺埋個肥婆<br />\n肥婆又唔做運動又懶，柔軟度應該好差，佢自己舉高隻腳都應該有難度，連提去90度都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就算提到<br />\n個男仔點頂佢對腳嘅重量<br />\n膊頭兩邊一定一齊pick pak甩較<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/205944_89a02bb3a158e3b77e8da1f2e3a370d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F205944_89a02bb3a158e3b77e8da1f2e3a370d3.jpg&h=3b0a40e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唯一得後入呢個pose係做到<br />\n但個屎忽咁多肉<br />\n要搵到個閪係邊都要成個鐘<br />\n到時都淋哂<br />\n仲要個肥婆咁懶，一定唔可以跪係度<br />\n只可以瞓係度<br />\n啲肉多到4,50摺<br />\n好似林雪咁<br />\n<br />\n仲有一定連叫都唔肯<br />\n唔做運動都算<br />\n點解仲唔忍下口<br />\n一叫一定成陣野食味<br />\n<br />\n一堆肉係張床到<br />\n應該會嫌要出汗又要郁嚟郁去<br />\n之後又要沖涼<br />\n應該玩震蛋就算<br />\n萬一放手左要搵翻粒震蛋又要多個鐘<br />\n結論係肥婆係唔適合有下一代<br />\n<br />\n仲有我提議應該所有同肥人拍拖嘅應該開個organization , 要當係NGO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bbd8e834cb145feab65647ba94961356300b63f","tid":306363,"uid":7948,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T13:01:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 肉酸post"},{"pid":"ade64397cb5f00422277b19cbc7677dfcc437219","tid":306363,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T13:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Cls 圖都有"},{"pid":"6e09d478839371c63993c96a253f8b6159cd0c0e","tid":306363,"uid":52728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T13:24:27.000Z","msg":"我諗左好耐都諗唔明，有無食用過肥婆嘅巴打可以話我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"539f04822455a07fc42c6fa2d2acb41d554f5b7f","tid":306363,"uid":675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T13:39:55.000Z","msg":"召喚心理時鐘"},{"pid":"08aaa35f981f347c1c05e41003f32c16b602a935","tid":306363,"uid":7367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T13:42:06.000Z","msg":"不如我地。。。。"},{"pid":"1fa630401af690c582b418cab94f76a543dc6705","tid":306363,"uid":52728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T13:55:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如我地。。。。</blockquote><br />\n做愛囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d106e753645515a23c897db983e2c1c1cd68352","tid":306363,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:11:23.000Z","msg":"用手撥開d肥肉就得，但碌鳩太短都唔得，會比肥肉頂住"},{"pid":"151b6634e68e9367f30ebe355e7822a68c48271e","tid":306363,"uid":114051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:44:05.000Z","msg":"肥既男人又點做 亞洲人條J較短 仲會俾個啤酒肚com住"},{"pid":"38ee0372c4cdecb6d3686672249c22cdd3368b3b","tid":306363,"uid":66252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:22:39.000Z","msg":"我今日都諗過呢個問題 就比我見到你呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又矮又肥既肥婆係點做愛？<br />\n事關我有個140cm都唔知有冇既同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"